{"tid":1082174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"遠離社交有冇問題？","createTime":"2019-03-28T19:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T01:16:03.000Z","uid":71730,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3b926176e1ead926edcfc8ca99548ff33ba9ad","tid":1082174,"uid":71730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人同我一樣，高中開始就keep住有拍拖，讀U，直至岀黎做野，中間係有離合過換過畫，但一直以黎都當身邊男/女朋友係最好朋友，有咩都會同佢講。<br />\n可能因為身邊一直有個人，都冇乜點同朋友維繫感情，個人都變得antisocial，覺得同朋友岀去都浪費時間，放工都係想拍下拖，或者留係屋企抖下多過同朋友岀去，whatsapp又懶覆，而好正路，好多本身熟既朋友，因為冇經常聯繫，漸漸都變得唔熟。<br />\n人地以為我好多朋友，但事實上冇乜邊個覺得特別熟，特別親密，我知自己衰既，冇乜維繫，懶，覺得維繫都係浪費精神時間。<br />\n有冇人同我一樣，遠離社交呢個諗法係咪好唔健康？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e07ea2eed4e4fd7e050d2ec2e6661b53828c39","tid":1082174,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"你唔驚你結婚冇人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dbef3ad7451919120b2cbca9f63914c5e7c720","tid":1082174,"uid":71730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e07ea2eed4e4fd7e050d2ec2e6661b53828c39","tid":1082174,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T19:36:03.000Z","msg":"你唔驚你結婚冇人去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T19:40:33.000Z","msg":"去就應該請到人去既，不過搵伴娘姊妹就頭痕啲...<br />\nBtw其實係咪一定要伴娘同姊妹呢？"},{"pid":"a16b5193d034dcb6c8fe3ba64d7d73d65dd1e5a5","tid":1082174,"uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T19:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CaXmU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCaXmU.jpg&h=e8b5b762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無～問～題～"},{"pid":"0b5bb0cd15cf8ad7f7243e17983ccad295a82a48","tid":1082174,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12dbef3ad7451919120b2cbca9f63914c5e7c720","tid":1082174,"uid":71730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e07